Introduction to Einstein Discovery

Einstein Discovery augments your business intelligence with statistical modeling and machine learning. It's integrated into Salesforce so you can operationalize data analysis, predictions, and improvements with clicks, not code.

Enhanced Analytics with Einstein Discovery

To use Einstein Discovery, your org must be provisioned with an applicable license, and user accounts must be assigned the appropriate permissions.
